    <titleShort>skaar rat</titleShort>
    <slot>Adulthood</slot>
    <bodyTypeMale>Male</bodyTypeMale>
    <bodyTypeFemale>Male</bodyTypeFemale>
    <baseDescription>Clan Skaar is famous for it's extensive mining operations, supplying greater clans with raw warpstone for profit and personal gain. [PAWN_nameDef] gained plenty of experience working for the clan, intimately familiar with the fineries of both mining and haggling.</baseDescription>
    <skillGains>
      <li>
        <defName>Mining</defName>
        <amount>2</amount>
