    <titleShort>skaul rat</titleShort>
    <slot>Adulthood</slot>
    <bodyTypeMale>Male</bodyTypeMale>
    <bodyTypeFemale>Male</bodyTypeFemale>
    <baseDescription>Almost the entirety of Clan Skaul is full of hedonists and addicts like [PAWN_nameDef], as the clan's main export is various warpstone narcotics, sold to both Skaven and man-things alike. Whether it's for potential profits or a potential high, [PAWN_nameDef] sees more value in drugs than anything else.</baseDescription>
